subject: Automobile Racing
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Tony Stewart and Carl Edwards battled for the Nascar Sprint Cup title throughout last season, and the Daytona 500 finds them prepared to do it again.
